{
  "stem": "24364.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I must say the first year in Palestine for me was the worst year of my whole life, because I was all alone.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents were gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And until then, I had still hope.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And, I don't know, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know what to do with myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I hadn't finished school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had no profession.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I stayed with my relatives for a while, but, you know, that was temporary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I decided [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that I might as well become a nurse, since I had worked in Mauritius.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And actually-- so I went to work in Afula, at a hospital as a nurse's aide, and sort of hoping that eventually I'll find a way somehow to go into nurse's training.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then something interfered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I forgot to mention that I had-- before I left Czechoslovakia, I had had an accident.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I tore the meniscus on my left knee.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so I had had surgery before I left Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And somehow, the surgery-- apparently, they didn't notice that I also had torn my cruciate ligament, and they didn't fix the cruciate ligament.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my knee was never the same.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I always had trouble after that surgery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so when I worked in the hospital as a nurse's aide, I-- very frequently, my-- my knee gave way.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so I talked to one of the doctors there, and they talked me into new surgery, and I stupidly went for it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the surgery, they put a-- they took a piece out of my tendon and tried to make an artificial cruciate ligament out of it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it really didn't work, so my knee has never been in good shape.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
